   "source": [
    "You can see that there is a positive correlation between the total steps and the calories burned, meaning that the more active we are (the more steps we take), the more calories we burn. Because of that, I want to determine if intensities impact the correlation as well."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "71fcd3be",
   "metadata": {
    "papermill": {
     "duration": 0.028159,
