     "start_time": "2024-03-04T09:14:46.626828",
     "status": "completed"
    },
    "tags": []
   },
   "source": [
    "The data shows that there are some users with no recorded data for very active minutes, so I will create a dataset that will omit rows containing the value of zero for VeryActiveMinutes. "
   ]
  },
